Others: South Africa vs Ireland 3rd ODI Match will be played on 7th October 2024.
South Africa vs Ireland 3rd ODI Match will be played at the Jaid Stadium in Abu Dhabi.
The match will start at 5 PM IST and the toss will take place 30 minutes prior to that.
The live streaming of South Africa vs Ireland 3rd ODI Match will be available on Fancode app and website.
